WEBVTT

00:00:19.440 --> 00:00:20.370
Would immortals

00:00:21.160 --> 00:00:22.670
Like bullets?

00:01:33.509 --> 00:01:35.170
I really didn't misjudge you.

00:01:37.060 --> 00:01:38.590
You're no ordinary person.

00:01:48.870 --> 00:01:49.789
Adjutant Mo.

00:01:51.009 --> 00:01:52.270
As for your dying wish,

00:01:53.280 --> 00:01:54.610
I'll fulfill it for you.

00:02:09.220 --> 00:02:12.080
"Wait until the three adjutants all meet their end,

00:02:12.900 --> 00:02:16.500
And even a single defeat could still accomplish the grand plan."

00:02:16.579 --> 00:02:18.250
This third adjutant

00:02:20.310 --> 00:02:22.170
Actually turned out to be myself.

00:02:22.340 --> 00:02:24.340
"Could accomplish the grand plan"—

00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:28.450
So I was just a pawn too.

00:02:31.970 --> 00:02:33.360
How ridiculous.

00:02:34.370 --> 00:02:36.280
How absurd.

00:02:40.910 --> 00:02:42.710
Everything was wrong all along.

00:07:00.550 --> 00:07:06.710
[Archives: The Nanyang Mystery]

00:07:07.070 --> 00:07:09.670
[Episode 31]

00:07:18.880 --> 00:07:19.940
Zhang Haixia!

00:07:21.770 --> 00:07:22.800
Zhang Haixia!

00:07:32.690 --> 00:07:33.500
Help me...

00:07:35.540 --> 00:07:36.810
Help me...

00:07:42.570 --> 00:07:43.630
Help me...

00:07:44.740 --> 00:07:45.930
Please...

00:07:46.740 --> 00:07:48.450
Please save us.

00:07:49.500 --> 00:07:50.750
Immortal.

00:07:54.240 --> 00:07:55.120
I'll do my best.

00:07:56.100 --> 00:07:57.560
The rest is up to your fate.

00:08:27.370 --> 00:08:29.700
I'm retired and still can't get any peace.

00:08:30.170 --> 00:08:31.960
Those two little brats—

00:08:45.900 --> 00:08:48.430
All grown up yet still won't let me worry less.

00:09:21.910 --> 00:09:22.940
We're saved!

00:09:22.940 --> 00:09:23.690
We're saved!

00:09:23.770 --> 00:09:24.580
We're saved!

00:09:24.580 --> 00:09:27.320
Feikun Balu saved us once again!

00:09:28.390 --> 00:09:29.420
He saved us!

00:10:01.770 --> 00:10:02.650
Mentor.

00:10:13.980 --> 00:10:15.310
You wretched disciple.

00:10:18.210 --> 00:10:21.410
Do you really think what you burned was the real medicine?

00:10:54.870 --> 00:10:56.400
This isn't what I intended.

00:10:57.020 --> 00:10:59.620
And it's also the outcome I least wanted to see.

00:11:00.610 --> 00:11:01.490
Mentor.

00:11:02.170 --> 00:11:03.570
I also want to go to Balai.

00:11:05.870 --> 00:11:07.470
Have you thought it through?

00:11:08.370 --> 00:11:09.240
I have.

00:11:13.750 --> 00:11:15.880
You've been this way since childhood,

00:11:16.480 --> 00:11:18.890
Always keeping everything bottled up inside.

00:11:18.890 --> 00:11:21.890
You need to think about yourself too, not just others.

00:11:23.400 --> 00:11:24.780
I was raised by you.

00:11:26.600 --> 00:11:27.840
Aren't you the same?

00:11:35.200 --> 00:11:36.530
If killing me

00:11:37.510 --> 00:11:38.710
Would bring you pain,

00:11:40.860 --> 00:11:43.460
Then I'd rather die on the way to kill Mo Yungao.

00:11:45.720 --> 00:11:46.720
Just treat it as

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:49.730
Me being willful one last time.

00:11:51.230 --> 00:11:52.420
Do as you please.

00:12:39.200 --> 00:12:39.860
Mentor.

00:13:02.640 --> 00:13:03.330
Mentor.

00:14:03.730 --> 00:14:05.270
This is great!

00:14:29.050 --> 00:14:30.180
Let's go take a look.

00:14:44.050 --> 00:14:45.240
Mentor...

00:14:59.340 --> 00:15:02.930
[2 days later]

00:16:16.920 --> 00:16:18.250
Let's give him some time

00:16:18.800 --> 00:16:20.660
To be alone with my mentor's wife.

00:16:44.390 --> 00:16:50.450
♪ Truth or lie, seasons pass in fleeting years ♪

00:16:51.540 --> 00:16:57.450
♪ A silent breeze brushes past that lingering warmth ♪

00:16:56.270 --> 00:16:59.050
Thank you, Feikun Balu!

00:16:58.810 --> 00:17:04.619
♪ In this fleeting world, I long for a moment of vivid life ♪

00:16:59.290 --> 00:17:01.740
Thank you, Feikun Balu!

00:17:02.340 --> 00:17:04.970
Thank you, Feikun Balu!

00:17:05.750 --> 00:17:08.200
Thank you, Feikun Balu!

00:17:06.050 --> 00:17:10.280
♪ I may have a chance to open a door ♪

00:17:08.619 --> 00:17:11.109
Thank you, Feikun Balu!

00:17:11.670 --> 00:17:18.240
♪ Where love and wish meet in a fleeting moment ♪

00:17:12.220 --> 00:17:15.010
Thank you, Feikun Balu!

00:17:15.140 --> 00:17:17.589
Thank you, Feikun Balu!

00:17:18.140 --> 00:17:20.619
Thank you, Feikun Balu!

00:17:19.190 --> 00:17:25.230
♪ There's no need to ask questions in the maze ♪

00:17:20.900 --> 00:17:23.520
Thank you, Feikun Balu!

00:17:23.660 --> 00:17:25.880
Thank you, Feikun Balu!

00:17:26.040 --> 00:17:28.280
♪ The world's bustle ♪

00:17:26.530 --> 00:17:28.900
Thank you, Feikun Balu!

00:17:29.030 --> 00:17:33.740
♪ Can briefly warm those under a shared roof ♪

00:17:29.380 --> 00:17:31.850
Thank you, Feikun Balu!

00:17:34.880 --> 00:17:40.160
♪ And the story has come to an end ♪

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:47.780
♪ Gifted to us the luck to walk side by side a stretch of way ♪

00:17:48.060 --> 00:17:54.530
♪ After partings and meetings, spring breeze comes round tomorrow ♪

00:17:55.130 --> 00:17:57.360
♪ The world's bustle ♪

00:17:58.010 --> 00:18:03.360
♪ Can keep whose dream under the roof? ♪

00:18:04.260 --> 00:18:14.690
♪ No farewell wishes needed in this life ♪

00:18:56.010 --> 00:18:57.030
What's going on?

00:18:57.050 --> 00:18:58.340
Why is he here?

00:18:59.720 --> 00:19:00.680
No idea.

00:19:02.350 --> 00:19:03.090
Everyone,

00:19:04.300 --> 00:19:05.960
We need to keep moving forward

00:19:06.480 --> 00:19:08.280
And complete the final mission.

00:19:08.320 --> 00:19:09.300
Where to?

00:19:10.970 --> 00:19:13.230
To fulfill your Commander's dying wish.

00:19:13.380 --> 00:19:14.740
Commander's already dead.

00:19:14.740 --> 00:19:16.140
You're not our adjutant.

00:19:16.160 --> 00:19:18.090
We don't have to follow his orders!

00:19:21.660 --> 00:19:22.460
You should know

00:19:22.460 --> 00:19:24.560
How Mo Yungao became the Commander—

00:19:25.720 --> 00:19:28.920
Because he discovered the secrets deep within Nanqiang.

00:19:31.280 --> 00:19:33.300
I can take you even deeper.

00:19:34.840 --> 00:19:37.100
As for who will become the next Mo Yungao,

00:19:39.330 --> 00:19:41.370
It's up to you.

00:19:49.130 --> 00:19:50.360
Let's go.

00:19:51.530 --> 00:19:52.330
That's right.

00:19:52.840 --> 00:19:54.240
I saw a group of warlords.

00:19:54.310 --> 00:19:56.040
They are in Nanqiang right now.

00:19:56.700 --> 00:19:57.460
Buddies,

00:19:57.590 --> 00:19:58.840
To protect Nanqiang,

00:19:59.110 --> 00:20:00.380
We have to kill them.

00:20:00.790 --> 00:20:01.510
-Yes. -That's right.

00:20:01.510 --> 00:20:02.000
You're right.

00:20:02.000 --> 00:20:02.850
Kill them!

00:20:02.850 --> 00:20:03.400
Kill them!

00:20:03.400 --> 00:20:03.880
Kill them!

00:20:03.880 --> 00:20:04.480
Kill them!

00:20:04.550 --> 00:20:05.180
Kill them!

00:20:05.180 --> 00:20:07.040
That friend of Master Feikun Balu

00:20:07.180 --> 00:20:08.400
Seems to be among them too,

00:20:08.400 --> 00:20:09.530
Named Zhang Haixia.

00:20:09.720 --> 00:20:10.750
What friend?

00:20:11.240 --> 00:20:12.830
He's that officer's second-in-command.

00:20:12.830 --> 00:20:13.420
That kind of scum

00:20:13.420 --> 00:20:14.790
Is not Mr. Zhang's friend.

00:20:14.790 --> 00:20:16.200
Then let's invite that "immortal"

00:20:16.200 --> 00:20:17.140
To come with us.

00:20:17.610 --> 00:20:19.220
Who the hell are you?

00:20:20.200 --> 00:20:21.730
Aren't you Mo Yungao's man?

00:20:22.570 --> 00:20:24.030
When did you sneak in here?

00:20:28.090 --> 00:20:29.470
Mr. Zhang saved me.

00:20:29.980 --> 00:20:31.980
I have forsaken darkness for light.

00:20:34.310 --> 00:20:37.040
Back then, Mo Yungao sought me out to go to Nanyang

00:20:37.660 --> 00:20:41.250
Because my family has raised snakes in Bailejing for generations.

00:20:41.250 --> 00:20:44.670
Mo Yungao had been researching the black-haired snake,

00:20:45.100 --> 00:20:48.030
And he needed a consultant who could control snakes.

00:20:48.770 --> 00:20:50.900
We heard about this from Zhang Hailou.

00:20:51.610 --> 00:20:53.050
So the Evil God of Nanyang

00:20:53.190 --> 00:20:56.650
Was something you guys were orchestrating behind the scenes.

00:20:56.680 --> 00:20:57.850
I was forced.

00:20:57.850 --> 00:20:59.290
If I didn't cooperate,

00:20:59.660 --> 00:21:01.190
He would have killed me too.

00:21:02.960 --> 00:21:03.960
Then tell me,

00:21:05.250 --> 00:21:07.180
How did you make the Evil God speak?

00:21:09.380 --> 00:21:11.580
T-This kind of snake is like a myna bird.

00:21:11.720 --> 00:21:13.720
It can mimic human speech by nature.

00:21:15.720 --> 00:21:16.720
Alright. Enough.

00:21:17.010 --> 00:21:18.510
That person you wanted to invite just now—

00:21:18.510 --> 00:21:19.710
He's not an immortal.

00:21:20.940 --> 00:21:22.340
His name is Zhang Hailou.

00:21:25.250 --> 00:21:27.340
Have you seen Zhang Hailou?

00:21:27.680 --> 00:21:28.310
No.

00:21:28.830 --> 00:21:30.890
He's not in the mourning hall either.

00:22:24.790 --> 00:22:26.570
Although I know you won't listen,

00:22:26.570 --> 00:22:28.510
I still advise you not to go looking for him.

00:22:28.510 --> 00:22:30.920
If something really is wrong with Zhang Haixia,

00:22:30.920 --> 00:22:32.610
Or even worse—if he has done evil—

00:22:32.610 --> 00:22:33.570
Then you'll have to face the situation

00:22:33.570 --> 00:22:36.160
Of whether you must kill him with your own hands.

00:22:36.160 --> 00:22:38.090
I don't think you'd be able to do it.

00:22:39.140 --> 00:22:40.460
Didn't you say that no matter what he did,

00:22:40.460 --> 00:22:41.380
You would forgive him,

00:22:41.380 --> 00:22:42.050
Clean up his mess for him,

00:22:42.050 --> 00:22:43.070
And take him home?

00:22:44.880 --> 00:22:46.790
Don't even think about looking for Zhang Haixia.

00:22:46.790 --> 00:22:48.440
He's no longer the person he used to be.

00:22:48.440 --> 00:22:50.410
If you can't realize this,

00:22:50.530 --> 00:22:52.730
Then it's better for you two not to meet.

00:23:35.790 --> 00:23:36.650
Macabre Masks—

00:23:37.510 --> 00:23:39.270
It's a tradition of the Zhang family.

00:23:39.270 --> 00:23:40.460
The older generation of the Zhang family,

00:23:40.460 --> 00:23:42.330
When they needed to carry out elimination of evil,

00:23:42.330 --> 00:23:44.300
Assassinations, or raids,

00:23:44.510 --> 00:23:46.840
Would wear masks designed by themselves.

00:23:47.420 --> 00:23:48.530
These masks

00:23:48.530 --> 00:23:50.050
Are not like human-skin masks

00:23:50.050 --> 00:23:51.470
And cannot be used for disguise.

00:23:51.470 --> 00:23:53.310
They are only meant to cover the face

00:23:53.310 --> 00:23:55.040
And intimidate the opponents.

00:23:55.090 --> 00:23:56.790
The Zhang family really has a lot of rules.

00:23:56.790 --> 00:23:59.070
Is it necessary to intimidate the opponents?

00:23:59.070 --> 00:24:01.530
The opponents we face are all very powerful,

00:24:02.030 --> 00:24:02.740
So the masks

00:24:02.740 --> 00:24:03.850
Are usually made to reflect

00:24:03.850 --> 00:24:05.660
The forms people fear most.

00:24:31.610 --> 00:24:34.090
We've been searching for ages and still can't find him.

00:24:34.090 --> 00:24:35.820
Where on earth did Mr. Zhang go?

00:24:37.420 --> 00:24:40.440
Mentor's wife's body is still lying in the ancestral hall.

00:24:40.440 --> 00:24:41.740
In the depths of Bailejing,

00:24:41.740 --> 00:24:43.530
Remnants of the Mo faction are still active.

00:24:43.530 --> 00:24:44.990
If we still can't find him,

00:24:45.460 --> 00:24:46.920
I will bury Mentor's wife.

00:24:46.940 --> 00:24:48.200
I'll handle it myself.

00:24:49.050 --> 00:24:50.250
Who's coming with me?

00:24:56.030 --> 00:24:57.770
But Zhang Haixia is still there.

00:24:57.770 --> 00:24:59.770
He's indeed difficult to deal with.

00:24:59.830 --> 00:25:01.490
Only Mr. Zhang knows him best.

00:25:01.700 --> 00:25:04.430
Where are the Mo faction remnants you mentioned?

00:25:07.250 --> 00:25:08.120
Are you okay?

00:25:08.740 --> 00:25:09.290
I'm fine.

00:25:10.140 --> 00:25:10.960
Just tell me directly

00:25:10.960 --> 00:25:11.960
Where the Mo faction remnants are.

00:25:11.960 --> 00:25:12.760
Zhang Hailou,

00:25:13.270 --> 00:25:14.530
You helped me avenge my deep grudge

00:25:14.530 --> 00:25:15.730
And saved Bailejing.

00:25:15.790 --> 00:25:16.880
Whatever you want to do,

00:25:16.880 --> 00:25:19.010
I'll definitely do my best to help you.

00:25:19.140 --> 00:25:19.770
Me too.

00:25:20.250 --> 00:25:22.510
My buddies and I are all at your disposal.

00:25:22.770 --> 00:25:23.560
Thank you.

00:25:23.770 --> 00:25:25.100
Regarding Zhang Haixia

00:25:25.220 --> 00:25:26.960
And those remnants of the Mo faction,

00:25:26.960 --> 00:25:28.290
We've found some clues.

00:25:29.930 --> 00:25:33.520
[Feikun Palu Temple]

00:25:32.330 --> 00:25:33.320
A few days ago,

00:25:33.440 --> 00:25:35.180
Someone saw remnants of the Mo faction

00:25:35.180 --> 00:25:37.180
Appear near the Feikun Balu Temple,

00:25:37.270 --> 00:25:38.800
But they soon disappeared.

00:25:39.070 --> 00:25:40.150
So I guess

00:25:40.350 --> 00:25:42.740
There's a deeper space under the Feikun Balu Temple,

00:25:42.740 --> 00:25:44.520
And it's related to the Zhang family.

00:25:44.520 --> 00:25:45.280
But

00:25:45.570 --> 00:25:47.170
We don't know where it leads.

00:26:07.770 --> 00:26:08.570
Zhang Hailou.

00:26:09.220 --> 00:26:10.580
If we find Zhang Haixia,

00:26:11.160 --> 00:26:12.360
What do you plan to do?

00:26:12.590 --> 00:26:13.650
Kill him.

00:27:00.610 --> 00:27:02.660
This should be the place built by the Zhang family ancestors

00:27:02.660 --> 00:27:04.420
To make medicine.

00:27:05.880 --> 00:27:08.420
There are also some ancient books and documents.

00:27:08.420 --> 00:27:09.680
They must be quite old.

00:27:10.880 --> 00:27:14.010
These probably date back to the Xia and Shang dynasties.

00:27:19.290 --> 00:27:21.220
So this is where Mentor used to come

00:27:21.570 --> 00:27:22.500
To gather herbs.

00:27:23.500 --> 00:27:25.160
It's just that all those herbs

00:27:25.480 --> 00:27:26.680
Have been destroyed.

00:27:26.810 --> 00:27:27.590
What herbs?

00:27:28.000 --> 00:27:29.730
The herbs to cure Zhang Haixia.

00:27:31.750 --> 00:27:33.880
He's no longer the person he used to be.

00:27:36.290 --> 00:27:37.820
There are some things here.

00:27:39.030 --> 00:27:40.490
They look freshly burned.

00:27:43.200 --> 00:27:44.530
Why would Zhang Haixia

00:27:44.660 --> 00:27:46.450
Go out of his way to burn these?

00:27:50.350 --> 00:27:51.480
Let's keep chasing.

00:28:24.640 --> 00:28:26.700
Are we going deep into the mountains?

00:28:28.070 --> 00:28:28.880
Big Pot.

00:28:29.960 --> 00:28:32.150
You seem very afraid of going into the mountains.

00:28:32.150 --> 00:28:33.330
It's not that I'm afraid.

00:28:33.330 --> 00:28:34.420
When I was racing horses back then,

00:28:34.420 --> 00:28:36.140
I once heard a legend from an old man

00:28:36.140 --> 00:28:37.330
In Nanqiang.

00:28:37.720 --> 00:28:38.440
Legend has it

00:28:38.440 --> 00:28:40.590
That deep in the mountains of Nanqiang,

00:28:40.590 --> 00:28:42.420
There lives a terrifying monster

00:28:42.420 --> 00:28:43.400
Called Atianre.

00:28:43.900 --> 00:28:45.070
This Atianre

00:28:45.160 --> 00:28:46.940
Was later defeated by the Mountain God.

00:28:46.940 --> 00:28:49.010
After the Mountain God killed Atianre,

00:28:49.010 --> 00:28:50.010
He set a rule

00:28:50.140 --> 00:28:51.570
That no descendant of Nanqiang

00:28:51.570 --> 00:28:53.000
Is allowed to enter the mountains.

00:28:53.000 --> 00:28:54.730
Because once someone enters,

00:28:54.790 --> 00:28:56.740
It will awaken the slumbering Atianre,

00:28:56.740 --> 00:28:59.140
And the entire Nanqiang will be destroyed.

00:28:59.530 --> 00:29:00.720
You said it yourself

00:29:00.720 --> 00:29:01.940
That it's a legend.

00:29:02.500 --> 00:29:03.610
I'm just curious—

00:29:04.290 --> 00:29:05.790
What exactly is Zhang Haixia

00:29:05.790 --> 00:29:07.070
Going in there to do?

00:29:08.530 --> 00:29:09.990
It can't be anything good.

00:29:10.160 --> 00:29:12.290
I won't sleep soundly until I kill him.

00:30:36.510 --> 00:30:38.370
The footprints have been erased.

00:30:38.410 --> 00:30:39.660
Which way did they go?

00:30:42.530 --> 00:30:43.160
This way.

00:30:46.750 --> 00:30:48.410
There are inscriptions here.

00:30:50.720 --> 00:30:51.290
These inscriptions

00:30:51.290 --> 00:30:53.160
Correspond to the danger of this crevice.

00:30:53.160 --> 00:30:54.420
Many of these crevices

00:30:54.550 --> 00:30:56.280
Were probably set up by people.

00:30:56.980 --> 00:30:58.040
They look very old.

00:30:58.090 --> 00:30:59.160
Do you recognize

00:30:59.660 --> 00:31:00.860
These inscriptions?

00:31:01.480 --> 00:31:03.790
Back when we were under the Southern Archives,

00:31:03.790 --> 00:31:05.330
There were similar crevices.

00:31:05.330 --> 00:31:06.990
They were all man-made traps,

00:31:07.070 --> 00:31:08.440
Each one unpredictable

00:31:08.550 --> 00:31:09.750
And extremely dangerous.

00:31:09.750 --> 00:31:11.850
It was the defense mechanism of the Southern Archives.

00:31:11.850 --> 00:31:13.250
Now that I think about it,

00:31:13.480 --> 00:31:14.590
It seems the Zhang family's ancestors

00:31:14.590 --> 00:31:16.390
Explored these places long ago,

00:31:16.500 --> 00:31:18.030
Then returned to the Archives

00:31:18.030 --> 00:31:20.490
And adopted these mechanisms for use later.

00:31:21.380 --> 00:31:22.460
These characters

00:31:22.750 --> 00:31:25.750
Look like oracle bone script or bronze inscriptions,

00:31:26.070 --> 00:31:27.530
But I'm not entirely sure.

00:31:28.290 --> 00:31:30.440
They seem to be from the Xia-Shang period—

00:31:30.440 --> 00:31:31.460
Possibly a very rare writing system

00:31:31.460 --> 00:31:33.350
Used by one of the Baiyue tribes.

00:31:33.610 --> 00:31:35.350
You're actually pretty cultured, huh?

00:31:35.350 --> 00:31:36.750
What kind of talk is that?

00:31:36.750 --> 00:31:37.640
I was a horse racer, okay?

00:31:37.640 --> 00:31:38.640
I've seen plenty.

00:31:40.500 --> 00:31:43.110
But why did Zhang Haixia have to come here

00:31:43.420 --> 00:31:45.020
To wipe away his footprints?

00:31:45.810 --> 00:31:46.640
Zhang Haixia,

00:31:47.250 --> 00:31:48.710
What exactly are you up to?

00:31:49.790 --> 00:31:50.660
Where are you?

00:31:52.840 --> 00:31:54.240
There's something here.

00:32:00.050 --> 00:32:00.980
[Heaven's Secret]

00:32:00.960 --> 00:32:02.660
It's Zhang Haixia's handwriting.

00:32:02.660 --> 00:32:07.480
[Mirror Lodge] [Mighty Lodge]

00:32:03.850 --> 00:32:05.130
He's warning me

00:32:05.310 --> 00:32:07.640
About the dangers hidden in each crevice.

00:32:07.880 --> 00:32:09.620
It seems he knew I was coming

00:32:10.250 --> 00:32:11.880
And deliberately left this for me.

00:32:11.880 --> 00:32:13.440
So this isn't his first time here.

00:32:13.440 --> 00:32:15.360
He even killed your mentor.

00:32:15.530 --> 00:32:18.070
Do you really think he'd be kind enough to leave you clues?

00:32:18.070 --> 00:32:19.200
Can that be trusted?

00:32:19.700 --> 00:32:21.000
But he didn't hurt you.

00:32:21.370 --> 00:32:24.800
[Mirror Lodge] [Mighty Lodge]

00:32:21.790 --> 00:32:22.570
Maybe

00:32:22.680 --> 00:32:24.940
He really left some useful clues inside.

00:32:25.420 --> 00:32:26.810
What if he set a trap?

00:32:27.480 --> 00:32:28.960
He even killed his own mentor.

00:32:28.960 --> 00:32:32.020
Who knows—he might end up killing Zhang Hailou as well.

00:32:35.440 --> 00:32:36.290
Although I don't know

00:32:36.290 --> 00:32:38.020
Where he got this information,

00:32:38.810 --> 00:32:39.750
I think

00:32:40.240 --> 00:32:42.240
He's trying to stall us and buy time.

00:32:43.080 --> 00:32:44.480
So we might as well burn it

00:32:44.850 --> 00:32:47.030
And not waste time thinking about it.

00:32:53.380 --> 00:32:55.840
Zhang Haixia is very good at anti-tracking.

00:32:56.070 --> 00:32:58.530
He'll erase all the traces he leaves behind.

00:32:58.980 --> 00:32:59.790
Snake Master,

00:33:00.050 --> 00:33:01.910
Can your snakes pick up his scent?

00:33:02.270 --> 00:33:02.940
Let me try.

00:33:18.250 --> 00:33:20.390
Every crevice has the smell of someone having entered,

00:33:20.390 --> 00:33:22.090
But the traces are all very faint.

00:33:22.090 --> 00:33:23.480
That's Zhang Haixia's style.

00:33:23.480 --> 00:33:24.450
Let's split up and search.

00:33:24.450 --> 00:33:25.500
It'll be faster.

00:33:26.380 --> 00:33:27.550
Once you find Zhang Haixia,

00:33:27.550 --> 00:33:29.480
Kill him immediately if possible.

00:33:30.060 --> 00:33:31.590
Otherwise, he'll kill you.

00:33:32.740 --> 00:33:34.250
Snake charmer, up ahead.

00:33:34.920 --> 00:33:35.530
Let's go.

00:33:35.530 --> 00:33:36.060
Let's go.

00:33:36.200 --> 00:33:36.660
Yes.

00:33:47.770 --> 00:33:49.230
Why are there so many jars?

00:33:50.830 --> 00:33:51.830
It really stinks.

00:33:53.480 --> 00:33:55.480
Looks like pickled vegetable jars.

00:34:03.850 --> 00:34:05.380
They've been dead for a while.

00:34:05.380 --> 00:34:06.710
Not Zhang Haixia's men.

00:34:07.140 --> 00:34:09.199
Probably villagers who wandered in.

00:34:09.980 --> 00:34:11.960
There are toxic spots. Died of poisoning.

00:34:11.960 --> 00:34:13.090
I heard

00:34:13.460 --> 00:34:15.940
That a long time ago in Nanqiang, there was a custom

00:34:15.940 --> 00:34:17.150
Where people would use

00:34:17.150 --> 00:34:18.750
Slaves as human sacrifices.

00:34:19.130 --> 00:34:21.130
After blood rituals, they would be placed into jars

00:34:21.130 --> 00:34:22.530
As offerings to the gods.

00:34:22.980 --> 00:34:25.239
So what's inside here are all offerings—

00:34:25.380 --> 00:34:26.580
Human bones and such.

00:34:31.650 --> 00:34:32.800
I feel like I've seen

00:34:33.260 --> 00:34:35.520
This kind of pattern in some file before.

00:34:41.630 --> 00:34:42.820
Why do you think these people

00:34:42.820 --> 00:34:44.920
All died in the same position?

00:34:56.860 --> 00:34:58.630
These jars contain a deadly poison.

00:34:58.630 --> 00:34:59.830
It seems these people

00:35:00.000 --> 00:35:03.260
All died from inhaling the toxic gas coming out of the jars.

00:35:06.650 --> 00:35:08.910
If they knew there was poison in the jars,

00:35:09.420 --> 00:35:10.940
Why would they still lean in to inhale?

00:35:10.940 --> 00:35:11.960
Two possibilities.

00:35:11.960 --> 00:35:14.590
One is that they committed a collective suicide.

00:35:14.590 --> 00:35:15.250
The other is

00:35:16.280 --> 00:35:17.960
That there must be something in these crevices

00:35:17.960 --> 00:35:19.160
Forcing them to do it.

00:35:20.290 --> 00:35:21.550
Keep your eyes peeled.

00:35:56.590 --> 00:35:57.440
Don't you feel

00:35:58.110 --> 00:35:59.110
It's a bit stuffy?

00:36:02.710 --> 00:36:04.360
Probably the air is too thin.

00:36:07.860 --> 00:36:09.390
Having trouble breathing?

00:36:11.360 --> 00:36:11.820
Come on.

00:36:32.390 --> 00:36:33.630
It seems these people all died

00:36:33.630 --> 00:36:35.430
Because of oxygen deprivation,

00:36:35.760 --> 00:36:38.400
And they tried to breathe the air inside the jars,

00:36:38.400 --> 00:36:40.130
But the jars contained poison.

00:36:40.690 --> 00:36:42.490
We need to pass through quickly.

00:36:52.710 --> 00:36:53.300
Qianjun.

00:36:55.490 --> 00:36:56.350
Zhang Qianjun.

00:37:28.340 --> 00:37:29.840
All I exhale is carbon dioxide.

00:37:29.840 --> 00:37:31.370
I can't hold on for too long.

00:37:31.820 --> 00:37:33.080
Move through quickly.

00:39:10.380 --> 00:39:12.760
You killed Zhang Haixia,

00:39:13.800 --> 00:39:15.610
And now you've killed me too.

00:39:16.340 --> 00:39:17.510
Are you satisfied?

00:39:18.380 --> 00:39:19.320
Mentor.

00:39:21.920 --> 00:39:22.900
Do you

00:39:25.000 --> 00:39:26.120
Regret it?

00:39:27.880 --> 00:39:28.590
If...

00:39:29.440 --> 00:39:31.300
Of course, you hate "if" the most.

00:39:35.800 --> 00:39:36.840
Then I might as well...

00:39:36.840 --> 00:39:38.930
Might as well end all of this.

00:39:39.150 --> 00:39:40.750
As long as you come over here,

00:39:41.260 --> 00:39:42.740
You can atone for your sins.

